Maintainer: Folu Akintola <folu.akintola@ndorms.ox.ac.uk>
Description: Streamlines the setup and execution of network studies using the 
    Observational Medical Outcomes Partnership (OMOP) Common Data Model (CDM). 
    Creates standardized project structures with template code, manages 
    dependencies with 'renv', provides code review utilities, and supports 
    containerized execution with 'Docker' for reproducible multi-site studies. 
    Includes 'GitHub' integration for collaboration and version control.
